comments: Huerter (ATL) makes contact to Harris' (BKN) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Reddish (ATL) has a legally collapsed forearm to Dinwiddie's (BKN) side that brushes his arm during his driving shot attempt. Reddish avoids making head contact.
Young (ATL) puts his a resting forearm on Prince's (BKN) chest during his driving shot attempt, but he does not extend it or apply force as Prince retreats.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Carter (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on Prince's (BKN) drive as Prince loses control of his dribble and the ball goes out of bounds.
Young (ATL) puts a resting hand on Prince's (BKN) chest during his play at the basket, but he does not extend his arm or apply force.
Bembry (ATL) hits Dinwiddie (BKN) on the head during his steal attempt.
Temple (BKN) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Young (ATL) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Hunter (ATL) commits a take foul on Prince (BKN).
Carter (ATL) commits a take foul on Harris (BKN).
